  "title": "HTTPConnection class¶",
  "content": "When you want to define dependencies that should be compatible with both HTTP and WebSockets, you can define a parameter that takes an HTTPConnection instead of a Request or a WebSocket.\n\nYou can import it from fastapi.requests:\n\nBases: Mapping[str, Any]\n\nA base class for incoming HTTP connections, that is used to provide any functionality that is common to both Request and WebSocket.",
